text: Rheingau-Taunus is a Kreis (district) in the west of Hesse, Germany. The district covers the western part of the Taunus mountains. The Rhine river forms the district's border in the south. ==Towns and municipalities== ===Towns=== #Bad Schwalbach #Eltville #Geisenheim #Idstein #Lorch #Oestrich- Winkel #Rüdesheim #Taunusstein ===Municipalities=== #Aarbergen #Heidenrod #Hohenstein #Hünstetten #Kiedrich #Niedernhausen #Schlangenbad #Waldems #Walluf ==References== Category:Districts of Hesse
